#ROOM
Vnum     11900
Name     &WThe Stockade Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here is heavy with the scent of damp stone and unwashed bodies.
Iron bars line the walls, and the sound of distant shouting and clashing
metal echoes from the halls ahead. This high-security prison was once 
under the control of Stormwind's finest, but the red bandanas tied to 
the torches suggest a new power has taken over.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    11046
Desc      The path back to the city canals.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11901
Desc      The main hallway leading deeper into the prison.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11901
Name     &WMain Hallway - Entry South&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The hallway is dimly lit by flickering torches. Debris from the recent
riot is scattered across the floor—broken benches, torn ledgers, and
discarded shackles. To the north, the hallway opens into a large
central hub.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11900
Desc      The prison entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11902
Desc      The hallway continues north.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11900 10 11901
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11902
Name     &WMain Hallway - Entry North&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The shouting grows louder here. Footprints in the dust indicate heavy
traffic moving between the wings. The stone walls are scarred by 
blade marks and scorch signs from magical fire.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11901
Desc      The hallway leads back to the entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11903
Desc      The central hub of the prison.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11901 10 11902
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11903
Name     &WThe Stockade Central Hub&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This large, circular chamber serves as the intersection for the three
main wings of the Stockade. To the west lies the block controlled by
the orcish prisoners. To the north, the main block where the rioters
hold the most ground. To the east, the wing occupied by the Dark
Iron saboteurs and the most dangerous criminals.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11902
Desc      The entry hallway.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11904
Desc      The entrance to the Left Wing.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11916
Desc      The entrance to the Middle Wing.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11928
Desc      The entrance to the Right Wing.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11902 10 11903
Reset M 0 11903 10 11903
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11904
Name     &RLeft Wing - West Corridor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air here is noticeably warmer. Rough orcish symbols have been
scrawled on the walls in blood. This wing is a maze of cells 
repurposed into a war camp.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11903
Desc      The central hub.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11905
Desc      The corridor continues west.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11901 10 11904
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11905
Name     &RLeft Wing - Guard Post&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small area where guards once monitored the cells. It is now a
mess of overturned tables and smashed lanterns.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11904
Desc      The corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11906
