Desc      The deep left corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11906
Name     &RLeft Wing - Cell Block A&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Small iron-barred cells line this room. Most of the doors have been
wrenched off their hinges, allowing the inmates to roam free.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11905
Desc      The guard post.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11900 10 11906
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11907
Name     &RLeft Wing - Cell Block B&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Piles of moldy straw serve as beds in these cramped quarters. The
stench of rot and sweat is overpowering.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11905
Desc      The guard post.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11901 10 11907
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11908
Name     &RLeft Wing - Deep Corridor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The path narrows as it descends slightly deeper. The sound of orcish
chanting can be heard from the end of the hall.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11905
Desc      The guard post.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
