#ROOM
Vnum     11915
Name     &RTargorr's Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This large room was once the warden's western office. It has been
converted into a throne room of sorts for Targorr the Dread. 
Skulls are mounted on the walls, and the floor is covered in
thick animal furs.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11912
Desc      The preparation area.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11905 1 11915
  Reset E 1 11916 1 16
  Reset G 1 11918 10
#ENDROOM

